{"talk":{"id":56012,"name":"Colette Pichon Battle: Climate change will displace millions. Here's how we prepare","description":"Scientists predict climate change will displace more than 180 million people by 2100 -- a crisis of \"climate migration\" the world isn't ready for, says disaster recovery lawyer and Louisiana native Colette Pichon Battle. In this passionate, lyrical talk, she urges us to radically restructure the economic and social systems that are driving climate migration -- and caused it in the first place -- and shares how we can cultivate collective resilience, better prepare before disaster strikes and advance human rights for all.","slug":"colette_pichon_battle_climate_change_will_displace_millions_here_s_how_we_prepare","recorded_at":"2019-12-04 00:00:00","published_at":"2020-01-10 15:47:43","updated_at":"2021-10-23 14:17:30","viewed_count":0,"emailed_count":0,"event":{"id":618,"name":"TEDWomen 2019"},"images":[{"image":{"size":"113x85","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/02c72d2e3bb344e32e81765319b113b45a99a071_113x85.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"240x180","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/02c72d2e3bb344e32e81765319b113b45a99a071_240x180.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"615x461","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/02c72d2e3bb344e32e81765319b113b45a99a071_615x461.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"2400x1800","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/02c72d2e3bb344e32e81765319b113b45a99a071_2400x1800.jpg"}}],"image_16x9":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/b959ea23db54517f428b208f335622a178b9ac38_2880x1620.jpg","media":{"internal":{"64k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/ColettePichonBattle_2019W-64k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":6370934,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"180k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/ColettePichonBattle_2019W-180k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":17615988,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"320k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/